<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white p-3 md:p-6"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls flower-matcher"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    <!-- ESERCIZI -->
    <div class="p-4 md:p-6 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg">
      <!-- Esercizio 10 -->
      <div class="p-4 mb-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <%= numero_esercizio_badge(10) %>
          Collega ogni operazione al suo risultato.
        </p>
        <div class="relative">
          <svg class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full pointer-events-none z-30" data-flower-matcher-target="canvas"></svg>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-around gap-3 mb-8 relative z-20">
            <% [
              { id: "op-1", pair: "p959", label: "8,6 + 0,99 =" },
              { id: "op-2", pair: "p761", label: "8,6 – 0,99 =" },
              { id: "op-3", pair: "p086", label: "8,6 × 0,1 =" },
              { id: "op-4", pair: "p86", label: "8,6 : 0,1 =" },
              { id: "op-5", pair: "p43", label: "8,6 × 0,5 =" },
              { id: "op-6", pair: "p215", label: "8,6 × 0,25 =" }
            ].each do |item| %>
              <div class="px-3 py-2 bg-cyan-100 rounded-lg text-center font-bold cursor-pointer hover:bg-cyan-200 transition"
                   data-action="click->flower-matcher#selectFlower"
                   data-flower-matcher-target="flower"
                   data-flower-id="<%= item[:id] %>"
                   data-pair="<%= item[:pair] %>"><%= item[:label] %></div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-around gap-3 relative z-20">
            <% [
              { id: "res-1", pair: "p761", label: "7,61" },
              { id: "res-2", pair: "p86", label: "86" },
              { id: "res-3", pair: "p959", label: "9,59" },
              { id: "res-4", pair: "p215", label: "2,15" },
              { id: "res-5", pair: "p086", label: "0,86" },
              { id: "res-6", pair: "p43", label: "4,3" }
            ].each do |item| %>
              <div class="px-3 py-2 bg-pink-100 rounded-lg text-center font-bold cursor-pointer hover:bg-pink-200 transition"
                   data-action="click->flower-matcher#selectFlower"
                   data-flower-matcher-target="flower"
                   data-flower-id="<%= item[:id] %>"
                   data-pair="<%= item[:pair] %>"><%= item[:label] %></div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 flex gap-3 items-center">
            <button class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold rounded-full w-8 h-8 transition flex items-center justify-center"
                    data-action="click->flower-matcher#reset" title="Ricomincia">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" />
              </svg>
            </button>
            <button class="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white font-bold rounded-full w-8 h-8 transition flex items-center justify-center"
                    data-action="click->flower-matcher#showSolutions" title="Soluzioni">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z" />
              </svg>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Esercizio 11 -->
      <div class="p-4 mb-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <%= numero_esercizio_badge(11) %>
          Completa le tabelle.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full border-collapse text-sm">
              <thead>
                <tr class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-100">
                  <th class="border-2 border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 p-2"></th>
                  <th class="border-2 border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 p-2">× 10</th>
                  <th class="border-2 border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 p-2">× 100</th>
                  <th class="border-2 border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 p-2">× 1 000</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2 font-bold text-center">3,15</td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="31,5" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="315" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="3150" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2 font-bold text-center">0,36</td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="3,6" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="36" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="360" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2 font-bold text-center">28</td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="280" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="2800" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="28000" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2 font-bold text-center">0,07</td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="0,7" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="7" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="70" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full border-collapse text-sm">
              <thead>
                <tr class="bg-green-100">
                  <th class="border-2 border-green-300 p-2"></th>
                  <th class="border-2 border-green-300 p-2">: 10</th>
                  <th class="border-2 border-green-300 p-2">: 100</th>
                  <th class="border-2 border-green-300 p-2">: 1 000</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2 font-bold text-center">874,5</td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="87,45" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="8,745" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="0,8745" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2 font-bold text-center">32</td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="3,2" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="0,32" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="0,032" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2 font-bold text-center">96,8</td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="9,68" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="0,968" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="0,0968" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2 font-bold text-center">15 700</td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="1570" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="157" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                  <td class="border-2 border-gray-300 p-2"><input type="text" data-correct-answer="15,7" class="w-full px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white"></td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- RISOLVI I PROBLEMI -->
      <div class="p-4">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-600 text-xl mb-6">RISOLVI I PROBLEMI</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="p-4 bg-cyan-50 rounded-lg">
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2"><%= numero_esercizio_badge(12) %></p>
            <p class="text-gray-800">
              Al supermercato Tommaso acquista una confezione di formaggio a 5,99 euro, una di prosciutto a 7,50 euro e una confezione di salmone a 6,65 euro. Se paga con una banconota da 50 euro, quanto riceve di resto?
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-cyan-50 rounded-lg">
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2"><%= numero_esercizio_badge(13) %></p>
            <p class="text-gray-800">
              In una pasticceria vengono confezionati 2 925 biscotti in sacchetti, ognuno dei quali ne contiene 45. Quanti sacchetti vengono confezionati? Ogni sacchetto viene venduto a 7,40 euro. Quanto incassa la pasticceria?
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-cyan-50 rounded-lg">
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2"><%= numero_esercizio_badge(14) %></p>
            <p class="text-gray-800">
              Una fioraia compra 15 dozzine di rose rosse e spende in tutto 216 euro. Quanto ha pagato ogni rosa?
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-cyan-50 rounded-lg">
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2"><%= numero_esercizio_badge(15) %></p>
            <p class="text-gray-800">
              Il proprietario di un caseificio deve travasare 285 litri di latte in bottiglie che contengono 0,75 litri ciascuna. Quante bottiglie potrà riempire?
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-cyan-50 rounded-lg">
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2"><%= numero_esercizio_badge(16) %></p>
            <p class="text-gray-800">
              In un anno Francesca ha speso 726 euro per la luce e 581,40 euro per il gas. Quanto ha speso in media ogni mese?
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-cyan-50 rounded-lg">
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2"><%= numero_esercizio_badge(17) %></p>
            <p class="text-gray-800">
              In un'azienda che produce marmellate devono essere confezionati 432 barattoli. 240 barattoli vengono messi in scatole da 16 barattoli ognuna, gli altri vengono messi in scatole che ne contengono 8. Quante scatole servono in tutto?
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-cyan-50 rounded-lg md:col-span-2">
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2"><%= numero_esercizio_badge(18) %></p>
            <p class="text-gray-800">
              In una fabbrica in un anno sono stati prodotti 522 000 bottoni. Il primo quadrimestre se ne vendono 132 599, il secondo 19 050 più del primo e il terzo quadrimestre 147 280. Quanti bottoni non sono stati venduti?
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- AllenaMente -->
        <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-yellow-200 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-bold text-red-600 mb-3">AllenaMente!</p>
          <p class="text-gray-800 mb-4">
            Anna, Paolo e Sara collezionano bandiere del mondo. Anna ha 20 bandiere, Paolo ne ha 6 meno di Sara, che ne ha 3 più di Anna. Quante bandiere ha ciascuno di loro?
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span>Anna ha</span>
              <input type="text" data-correct-answer="20" class="w-16 px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white">
              <span>bandiere.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span>Paolo ha</span>
              <input type="text" data-correct-answer="17" class="w-16 px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white">
              <span>bandiere.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span>Sara ha</span>
              <input type="text" data-correct-answer="23" class="w-16 px-2 py-1 border-2 border-pink-400 rounded text-center font-bold bg-white">
              <span>bandiere.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
  </div>
</div>
